## ğŸ Known Issues

- **Multi-monitor support is inconsistent:** AutoShorts may not always work as expected when Chrome is moved between monitors with different scaling or DPI settings.
- **YouTube tab focus required:** The extension only works reliably when the YouTube Shorts tab is focused. If the tab is not active, auto-skip and stats tracking may not function.

